text: Yhonathan Alexander Yustiz Linarez (born 27 January 1992) is a Venezuelan footballer who plays as a goalkeeper for Aragua F.C. in the Venezuelan Primera División. ==References== ==External links== *Profile at World Football Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Caracas FC players Category:Aragua FC players Category:Venezuelan Primera División players Category:Venezuelan footballers Category:Association football goalkeepers Category:People from Maracay
